          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. Complexity Level: Medium"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure involves multiple steps, including logging, conditional logic for adjusting parameters, and a complex SQL query with multiple joins and subqueries. The complexity arises from the need to handle dynamic date ranges and ensure accurate reporting of billing data."
        }
